OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778170273
OL,3,CSouthampton General Hospital facing
OL,4,C'significant pressure'
OL,6,FUniversity Hospital Southampton is
OL,7,Furging the public to use its services
OL,8,Fwisely, as it continues to recover
OL,9,Ffrom a major fire earlier this year.
OL,11,FThe site's endoscopy unit was badly
OL,12,Fdamaged, and several wards had to be
OL,13,Fclosed in February this year,
OL,14,Ffollowing the blaze.
OL,16,FThe NHS is in the process of reopening
OL,17,Fthe damaged areas, but the hospital
OL,18,Ftrust says the lack of space and loss
OL,19,Fof resources is compounding pressures
OL,20,Fon the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
