PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778170273
OL,3,CSouthampton General Hospital facing
OL,4,C'significant pressure'
OL,6,FSites run by the trust, including
OL,7,FSouthampton General, are currently
OL,8,Fvery busy and staff are working hard
OL,9,Fto manage demand.
OL,11,FIt's asking members of the public to
OL,12,Fonly attend Southampton General's
OL,13,Femergency department (A&E) if they
OL,14,Fhave a life-threatening condition, to
OL,15,Fensure care can be given to those who
OL,16,Fneed it most.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
