OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778170273
OL,3,CSouthampton General Hospital facing
OL,4,C'significant pressure'
OL,6,FHealth bosses are also asking
OL,7,Frelatives of patients, collecting them
OL,8,Ffrom the site, to ensure they do so as
OL,9,Fsoon as possible after a discharge is
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FThis will help the trust to free up
OL,13,Fspace in wards, so others can be
OL,14,Ftreated.
OL,16,FPeople who are in need of urgent
OL,17,Fhealth advice are being asked to use
OL,18,FNHS 111, contact their GP, or go to an
OL,19,FUrgent Treatment Centre.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
