OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778170273
OL,3,CSouthampton General Hospital facing
OL,4,C'significant pressure'
OL,6,FIn a statement, the hospital said:
OL,7,F"Our hospitals are currently very
OL,8,Fbusy. We continue to face significant
OL,9,Fpressure as we recover from a
OL,10,Fsignificant fire at Southampton
OL,11,FGeneral Hospital in February.
OL,13,F"Our teams are working incredibly hard
OL,14,Fto safely discharge patients who are
OL,15,Fready to go home.
OL,17,F"Your support makes a real difference
OL,18,Fand helps us care for those who need
OL,19,Fus most."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
